 "remarks": "Nestled on a picturesque property with protected open space directly across the street, 31 Vista Road offers privacy, charm, and flexibility in a convenient Wilton location just minutes to both Wilton Center and Ridgefield&apos;s vibrant shops and restaurants. Lovingly maintained, this inviting home blends timeless character with everyday comfort, featuring hardwood floors, exposed beams, a welcoming family room with fireplace, and an open dining area ideal for gathering. The eat-in kitchen overlooks the peaceful backyard and showcases its original vintage 1961 countertops alongside stainless steel appliances and abundant cabinetry. The **second-floor addition, completed in 2008,** added two spacious bedrooms, a full bath with a thoughtfully designed separate vanity and shower/WC layout, and a generous den connected by a spiral staircase to a finished 27&apos; x 15&apos; loft with standing headroom-ideal for recreation, hobbies, or storage. Surrounded by mature trees and level lawn, this special property offers the perfect balance of nature, convenience, and classic New England charm.",
